CDFglobalAttributes.PI_name: V. Angelopoulos, J. Bonnell & F. Mozer
CDFglobalAttributes.TITLE: Electric Field Instrument (EFI) Measurements
CDFglobalAttributes.TEXT: THEMIS-C: Electric Field Instrument (EFI) Electric field measurements. The L2 product is a 3D estimate of Eperp derived from the spin plane E-field measurements assuming E dot B = 0, using relevant FGM (Flux-Gate Magnetometer) data.Includes spin-averaged, and Fast-survey field data.Spin-averaged (EFS_DOT0) data has approximately 3 second time resolution. Fast-survey (EFF_DOT0) data has 1/8 second time resolution.
